  "text": "A study of this nature, where approximation schemes are developed for bin packing type problems, and in particular, where the complexity of such a problem is completely resolved by designing an AFPTAS, is an established direction of research. Studies of similar flavor were widely conducted for other variants of bin packing, see e.g. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
